      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;print--play-variants-and-challenges&#34;&gt;Print &amp;amp; Play, Variants, and Challenges&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://automafactory.com/rr-youtoma/&#34;&gt;Youtoma&lt;/a&gt;: An alternative solo mode for Rolling Realms.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/148450/endless-nightmare&#34;&gt;Endless Nightmare&lt;/a&gt;: A free print and play game designed by Morten Monrad Pedersen for the 2013 Solitaire Print and Play Contest. No cutting or papercrafting required. Morten&amp;rsquo;s game &lt;a href=&#34;https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/366322/skoventyr&#34;&gt;Skoventyr&lt;/a&gt; started out as an attempt to reimplement Endless Nightmare with mechanics from one of his favorite games, &lt;a href=&#34;https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/156336/onirim-second-edition&#34;&gt;Onirim&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://boardgamegeek.com/thread/3218395/skoventyr-challenge-january-2024-base-game&#34;&gt;Skoventyr challenges&lt;/a&gt;: 12 challenges for Skoventyr designed by &lt;a href=&#34;https://boardgamegeek.com/user/Newsh&#34;&gt;Paul Newsham&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://boardgamegeek.com/thread/2811510/a-simple-variant-for-making-the-solo-mode-more-lik&#34;&gt;A variant for the Floriferous solo mode&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
